        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Luna and Hidalgo Counties Wilderness Study Area Release Act of 2015</b></p> <p> Releases specified wilderness study areas in the Luna and Hidalgo Counties in New Mexico from further study for designation as wilderness. </p>]]></text>
